nodes.text: I4-M9 was a droid that was owned by the Shistavanen Blik during the time of the Clone Wars. When Blik traveled to the planet Caarimon, he brought I4 with him, aboard his starship, the Ku'Amo. However, due to space limitations aboard the Ku'Amo, I4 had to remain deactivated while he was aboard it.
